The paper proposes a new model for generative modeling of matrix data, specifically for image super-resolution and handwritten digit recognition. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and multimedia (cs.MM).
